{"id":10,"date":"2017-07-07T19:07:09","date_gmt":"2017-07-07T19:07:09","guid":{"rendered":"http:\/\/hoodbuilder.dev\/?page_id=10"},"modified":"2023-10-28T09:47:15","modified_gmt":"2023-10-28T09:47:15","slug":"about-us","status":"publish","type":"page","link":"https:\/\/www.hoodbuilder.com\/about-us\/","title":{"rendered":"About Us"},"content":{"rendered":"<div class=\"wpb-content-wrapper\"><p>[vc_row][vc_column]<div class=\"ult-spacer spacer-685e562179715\" data-id=\"685e562179715\" data-height=\"95\" data-height-mobile=\"60\" data-height-tab=\"\" data-height-tab-portrait=\"\" data-height-mobile-landscape=\"60\" style=\"clear:both;display:block;\"><\/div>[\/vc_column][vc_column el_class=&#8221;wps-left-column&#8221; offset=&#8221;vc_col-lg-6 vc_col-md-6&#8243;][vc_column_text]<\/p>\n<h4>About Hood Builder<\/h4>\n<p><span class=\"big-para-blue\">Hood Builder Bio <a href=\"https:\/\/www.hoodbuilder.com\/services\/hvac\/ventilation\/\">Green Ventilation Systems<\/a>, Inc.\u2122 is the leading distribution, fabrication, and installation company for food facilities of any size. We have offices and plants across the United States that enable us to help you with all of your <a href=\"https:\/\/www.hoodbuilder.com\/services\/restaurant-services\/construction\/\">construction<\/a>, <a href=\"https:\/\/www.hoodbuilder.com\/services\/hoods\/cleaning\/\">cleaning<\/a> or maintenance needs, no matter where you happen to be located.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/www.hoodbuilder.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/07\/content-img-aboutus.jpg\" alt=\"Restaurant Construction Los Angeles | Hood Installation Denver | Hvac Los Angeles\" class=\"aligncenter wp-image-132 size-full\" title=\"Hood Installation Los Angeles | Restaurant Construction Denver | Hvac Denver\" width=\"710\" height=\"260\" srcset=\"https:\/\/www.hoodbuilder.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/07\/content-img-aboutus.jpg 710w, https:\/\/www.hoodbuilder.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/07\/content-img-aboutus-300x110.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 710px) 100vw, 710px\" \/><\/p>\n<p>For over 25 years, we have been providing our clients with quality service and topmost care. From turnkey restaurant construction to <a href=\"https:\/\/www.hoodbuilder.com\/services\/hoods\/installation\/\">hood installation and maintenance<\/a>, food trucks and <a href=\"https:\/\/www.hoodbuilder.com\/services\/hvac\/air-conditioning\/\">HVAC maintenance and service<\/a>, Hood Builder has you covered.[\/vc_column_text][\/vc_column][vc_column el_class=&#8221;wps-right-column&#8221; offset=&#8221;vc_col-lg-6 vc_col-md-6&#8243;][vc_column_text]<\/p>\n<h4>Any Sized Facility, Anywhere in the Country<\/h4>\n<p>We have worked with some of the biggest names in business, including McDonald\u2019s, PepsiCo, Applebee\u2019s, Mayo Clinic, Olive Garden, British Airways, 3M, FedEx, John Deere, The Home Depot and many more.<\/p>\n<p>We sell all systems and brands, are experts in design and fabrication, and we install all systems to your exact specifications. Our leading team of mechanical, electrical, and structural experts and contractors will exceed your expectations while providing you with everything you need to get your business up and running at optimum performance.<\/p>\n<p>When you want quality service from a leading team of experts at competitive pricing, your only choice should be Hood Builder. You can begin by requesting a full quote for our services. Once you decide to work with us, we will begin by first understanding your commercial contracting needs. Our job is to give you the confidence that the kind of work we perform will exceed all of our competitors.<\/p>\n<p>Like our other clients, you come to prefer us for our competitive pricing, quality of service, and the fact that you can turn to us for all of your mechanical, electrical, structural and fire suppression requirements.<\/p>\n<p><strong>For a full and fast price quote, contact Hood Builder today at (800) 750-7055.<\/strong>[\/vc_column_text][\/vc_column][vc_column]<div class=\"ult-spacer spacer-685e562179729\" data-id=\"685e562179729\" data-height=\"115\" data-height-mobile=\"60\" data-height-tab=\"\" data-height-tab-portrait=\"\" data-height-mobile-landscape=\"60\" style=\"clear:both;display:block;\"><\/div>[\/vc_column][\/vc_row][vc_row full_width=&#8221;wps-full-width&#8221;][vc_column][wps_featured_text_content content_type=&#8221;style3&#8243; image=&#8221;137&#8243; section_title=&#8221;Full Construction and Remodelling Services &#8220;]<span class=\"big-para\">We do plans, city approvals, full construction and remodelling for facilities of any size and location nationwide.<\/span><\/p>\n<ul>\n<li>Restaurant Construction<\/li>\n<li>Food Truck Construction<\/li>\n<li>Commercial Kitchen Hoods<\/li>\n<li>Fire Suppression Systems<\/li>\n<li>Cleaning &amp; Maintenance<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p>[\/wps_featured_text_content][\/vc_column][\/vc_row][vc_row full_width=&#8221;wps-full-width&#8221;][vc_column]<div class=\"templatera_shortcode\"><div id=\"get-quote-form\" class=\"wps-row-container vc_row wpb_row vc_row-fluid vc_custom_1505174015547 vc_row-no-padding vc_row-fluid wps-vc-fullwidth\" ><div class=\"container wps-vc-container\"><div class=\"wpb_column vc_column_container vc_col-sm-12\"><div class=\"vc_column-inner \"><div class=\"wpb_wrapper\"><div class=\"ult-spacer spacer-685e56217a0fa\" data-id=\"685e56217a0fa\" data-height=\"150\" data-height-mobile=\"70\" data-height-tab=\"\" data-height-tab-portrait=\"\" data-height-mobile-landscape=\"70\" style=\"clear:both;display:block;\"><\/div><\/div><\/div><\/div><div class=\"wps-left-column get-free-q-desc wpb_column vc_column_container vc_col-sm-12 vc_col-md-6\"><div class=\"vc_column-inner \"><div class=\"wpb_wrapper\">\n<div class=\"wps-homepage-get-free-quote-wrap\">\n    <div class=\"meet-the-doctor-details\">\n        <div class=\"h2tospan\">\n            <span>Get a Free Quote<\/span>\n        <\/div>\n        <div class=\"section-description\">\n\t\t\t<p><span class=\"big-para\">We\u2019ve got you covered. Hood Builder is a leading distribution, fabrication, and installation company for food facilities of any size. We have offices and plants across the United States that are ready to tend to your needs.<\/span><\/p>\n<p>If you intend on receiving quotes from other installers in the industry, please be sure to compare the items included in the package in addition to price and reputation. Our objective is to always be your obvious choice. Please fill out the form below and and we will prepare a quote.<\/p>\n<p><strong>For a Full and Fast price Quote, Contact Hood Builder today at <a href=\"tel:+1-303-777-7720\">303-777-7720<\/a>.<\/strong><\/p>\n        <\/div>\n    <\/div>\n<\/div>\n\n\n\n\n<\/div><\/div><\/div><div class=\"wps-get-free-quote-form get-free-q-frm wpb_column vc_column_container vc_col-sm-12 vc_col-md-6\"><div class=\"vc_column-inner \"><div class=\"wpb_wrapper\">\n<div class=\"wpcf7 no-js\" id=\"wpcf7-f4-o1\" lang=\"en-US\" dir=\"ltr\" data-wpcf7-id=\"4\">\n<div class=\"screen-reader-response\"><p role=\"status\" aria-live=\"polite\" aria-atomic=\"true\"><\/p> <ul><\/ul><\/div>\n<form action=\"\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/pages\/10#wpcf7-f4-o1\" method=\"post\" class=\"wpcf7-form init\" aria-label=\"Contact form\" enctype=\"multipart\/form-data\" novalidate=\"novalidate\" data-status=\"init\">\n<div style=\"display: none;\">\n<input type=\"hidden\" name=\"_wpcf7\" value=\"4\" \/>\n<input type=\"hidden\" name=\"_wpcf7_version\" value=\"6.0.5\" \/>\n<input type=\"hidden\" name=\"_wpcf7_locale\" value=\"en_US\" \/>\n<input type=\"hidden\" name=\"_wpcf7_unit_tag\" value=\"wpcf7-f4-o1\" \/>\n<input type=\"hidden\" name=\"_wpcf7_container_post\" value=\"0\" \/>\n<input type=\"hidden\" name=\"_wpcf7_posted_data_hash\" value=\"\" \/>\n<\/div>\n<div class=\"row wps-form-row\">\n\t<div class=\"col-sm-6 input-field\">\n\t\t<p><span class=\"wpcf7-form-control-wrap\" data-name=\